(x_1,y_1),...,(x_n,y_n)\in \mathbb{R}^2  
x_i\neq x_j
i\neq j
p
p(x_k)=y_k ,\forall k=1,...,n
\det\begin{pmatrix}  p(x)& 1 & x & x^2 &\dots & x^n \\ y_0 & 1 & x_0 & x_0^2 &\dots &x_0^n \\ y_1 & 1 & x_1 & x_1^2 &\dots &x_1^n \\ \vdots & & & & & \vdots \\ y_n & 1 & x_n & x_n^2 &\dots & x_n^n  \end{pmatrix}=0. 
